of treating the Xue family.

57
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:45,360
Two years ago,
on the eighth night of December,

58
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,680
I was hurriedly called
to the Xue's mansion.

59
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:49,120
There can be no mistake.

60
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:50,960
Are you sure?

61
