I have suffered.

85
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,959
No amount of wealth and honor

86
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:32,199
can buy off justice and morality,

87
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,040
nor can it make me forget

88
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:37,079
that the Xue family and the Rong family
betrayed me,

89
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:39,279
wronged me, insulted me,

90
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,519
and tried to kill me three times

91
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,800
in the name of rites and norms.

92
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:52,800
