93
00:04:59,639 --> 00:05:01,079
It's a murder case
you are talking about.

94
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,720
It should be handled
by government officials.

95
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:06,240
There is nothing I can do
about this matter.

96
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,759
Let's see

97
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,920
who is willing to take this case.

98
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,959
Your Grace,

99
