I-I can also testify.

104
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,199
There are witnesses available.

105
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:49,199
I, Li Ang, from the Ministry of Justice,
am willing to take on this case.

106
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,600
I am also willing to handle it.

107
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,160
Me too.

108
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,839
I am willing to testify.

109
00:05:57,959 --> 00:05:59,959
I beg for your mercy, Your Grace.

110
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,040
At your request,

111
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:16,040
I won't let you take my reward

112
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,680
in the name of Gong Wan'er.

113
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,800
Once the case is concluded,

114
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,959
the truth comes to light,

115
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,199
and the guilty face justice,

116
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,879
I will personally put this hairpin

117
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:31,199
on Xue Wan'er.

118
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:51,959
Thank you, Your Grace.

119
